Class Merge

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.exasol.sql.AbstractFragment
      • com.exasol.sql.dml.merge.Merge
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MergeFragment, Fragment, SqlStatement
    public class Merge
extends AbstractFragment
implements SqlStatement, MergeFragment
    This class implements an SQL Merge statement which is a combination of INSERT, UPDATE and DELETE.
